CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 12, 1963, pg. 5, reads: "Open Howell Headquarters - Large... [illegible] the opening of Citizen's Headquarters for William Howell, GOP candidate for City Controller. The headquarters are located at 2127 Centre Ave. in the Fifth Ward. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Campaign headquarters for William S. Howell for City Controller, with three women and child standing in doorway, 2127 Centre Avenue, Hill District
